                                         "text":  "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgPlanckCMB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPlanckCMB', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figura 1</b>: Mapa da radiação cósmica de fundo (<htcite0>).</p>",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "6006cb3a-9409-4d2a-999c-e4c74249f563",
                                                            "text":  "ESA",
